<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="color-scheme" content="dark" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-dark-5@1.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap-night.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/styles.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/styles-fale-conosco.css" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.9.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('./partials/header') %>

    <main>
      <section class="descricao-fale-conosco">
        <p class="text-center">
          Precisa entrar em contato com a gente?, Verifique se as nossas páginas
          respondem a sua pergunta. Caso contrário, preencha o formulário abaixo
          do Fale Conosco ou utilize os demais canais para o envio de sugestões,
          reclamações, elogios, solicitações e informações/dúvidas.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="formulario">
        <form>
          <div class="nome-email">
            <div class="nome">
              <div class="input-group mb-3">
                <div class="input-group-prepend">
                  <span class="input-group-text" id="basic-addon1">@</span>
                </div>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="nome"
                  name="nome"
                  required
                  type="text"
                  class="form-control"
                  placeholder="Username"
                  aria-label="Username"
                  aria-describedby="basic-addon1"
                />
              </div>
              <div class="input-group mb-3">
                <input
                  type="email"
                  id="email"
                  name="email"
                  required
                  type="text"
                  class="form-control"
                  placeholder="e-mail"
                  aria-label="Recipient's username"
                  aria-describedby="basic-addon2"
                />
                <div class="input-group-append">
                  <span class="input-group-text" id="basic-addon2"
                    >@exemplo.com</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
              </div>
              <div class="input-group">
                <div class="input-group-prepend">
                  <span class="input-group-text">Insira Sua mensagem</span>
                </div>
                <textarea class="form-control" aria-label="Insira Sua mensagem"></textarea>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="enviar">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Enviar</button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
    <script 
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" 
      integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" 
      crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
